about.summary: A Python library with convenience helpers for working with the AWS Serverless Application Repository.

name: serverlessrepo
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "serverlessrepo" %}
{% set version = "0.1.10" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 671f48038123f121437b717ed51f253a55775590f00fbab6fbc6a01f8d05c017

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - boto3 >=1.9,<2
    - python
    - pyyaml >=5.1,<6
    - six >=1.11,<2

test:
  imports:
    - serverlessrepo
    - tests.unit

about:
  home: "https://github.com/awslabs/aws-serverlessrepo-python"
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "A Python library with convenience helpers for working with the AWS Serverless Application Repository."
  doc_url: "https://aws.amazon.com/serverless/serverlessrepo/"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/awslabs/aws-serverlessrepo-python"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rluria14
    - oblute
    - ndmaxar
